          { type: 'text', content: '<p>The SRH and DC matchups remain MI\'s comfort zones. A combined 9-2 (81.8%) against these two teams provides a reliable points floor. If MI can maintain that dominance while improving against GT (2-5) and LSG (2-4), the arithmetic changes significantly.</p>' }
