          { type: 'text', content: '<p><strong>What the Auction Tells You:</strong> CSK are building two teams simultaneously. One is the 2026 XI, Samson, Gaikwad, Dube, Brevis, Noor Ahmad, Khaleel, designed to compete now. The other is the 2027+ squad, Prashant Veer, Kartik Sharma, Ayush Mhatre, Gurjapneet Singh, designed to thrive after the transition is complete. It\'s a franchise that has always thought in cycles, not seasons. This auction is the beginning of the next cycle.</p>' },
          { type: 'text', content: '<p><strong>Auction Grade: B-.</strong> The Samson trade is an A+ move that gives CSK their post-Dhoni identity. The retention core (Noor Ahmad, Khaleel, Gaikwad, Dube) provides proven quality. The 28.40 Cr on Prashant Veer and Kartik Sharma is either a D or an A, there is no middle ground, and we won\'t know which until May.</p>' }
