          { type: 'text', content: '<p>Unlike many franchises, KKR\'s innings context split is remarkably balanced. The powerplay is slightly more aggressive when chasing (+2.1 SR), while the death overs show a 5.2-point decline when chasing, likely reflecting the loss of wickets earlier in the innings that depletes the finishing options. The middle overs are virtually identical, suggesting the team\'s approach doesn\'t meaningfully change based on innings context.</p>' }
