          { type: 'text', content: '<p><strong>All-Time: 120-115 (51.1% win rate)</strong></p>' },
          { type: 'text', content: '<p>The Punjab Kings reversal is the most significant trend. KKR\'s all-time record of 21-13 (60.0%) against PBKS has inverted to 1-3 since 2023. Harshit Rana\'s 12.17 economy in 4 matches against PBKS and Narine\'s relatively quiet 87 runs in 4 innings (212.2 SR but only 41 balls, LOW) suggest KKR haven\'t figured out PBKS\'s rebuilt squad. Conversely, the RCB matchup has shifted from 57.1% all-time to 80.0% since 2023, driven by Varun\'s 9 wickets at 8.04 economy in 5 matches against RCB.</p>' }
