          { type: 'text', content: '<p><strong>5. Pathirana\'s Middle-Overs Economy Is the Surprise</strong></p>' },
          { type: 'text', content: '<p>Matheesha Pathirana is known as a death specialist, but his middle-overs economy of 8.35 across 46 overs (MEDIUM) is actually stronger than his death economy of 9.46 (64.2 overs, MEDIUM). In the middle overs, he takes 12 wickets at 35.1% dot ball rate and 14.1% boundary conceded rate. The slower-ball variations that make him lethal at the death are equally effective when batters are trying to rotate strike. KKR\'s coaching staff should consider deploying him for 1-2 middle overs to complement Narine and Varun, not just hoarding all 4 overs for the death.</p>' }
