          { type: 'text', content: '<p>The SRH matchup is the one that should concern the coaching staff most. A 1-4 record since 2023, combined with SRH\'s aggressive batting approach that specifically targets death bowling, plays directly into RR\'s worst phase. Conversely, the CSK turnaround (4-1 since 2023 against an all-time 15-16 record) shows RR can dominate specific matchups when conditions favour their strengths.</p>' }
